    Create Configuration And Watch Files
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/*  
|   *   Run the following command to start the TypeScript compiler in watch mode
|   tsc --watch file.ts
|   *   To initialize a TypeScript configuration file, you can use the
|   tsc --init
|   *   Enable Some Config Tsk in Config File :
|   rootDir, sourceMap, outDir, removeComments 
*/